

1.1. The system shall have a well documented guide released with every increment for users’ ease.
     1.1.1. The document shall have installation and online use guidelines for web and mobile platforms.
     1.1.2. The document shall show all the words in the word bank that correspond to the available objects for story.
     1.1.3. The document shall show the interpretation of every word included in the word bank in an alphabetical order.
     1.1.4. The document shall categorize all the words included in the word bank under the noun, verb, adverb,adjective and preposition in alphabetical order.
     1.1.5. The document shall provide a stepwise procedure for using the animation tool.
     1.1.6. The document shall contain 10 story scenarios for the user to understand how the tool works.
     1.1.7. The document shall list the extensions to download to avail the audio feature.
     1.1.8. The document shall state the deployment guideline and the environment required to use the tool.

1.2. The system shall have tutorials that explain the use of every offered feature.
     1.2.1. The document shall contain links under along with each feature description that redirects to the corresponding tutorial.
     1.2.2. The document shall contain tutorials for all 10 story scenarios that are provided for the user's understanding.
     1.2.3. The tutorial video shall contain the watermark of the animation tool’s logo.

1.3. The system shall have a test manual for quality analysis after every increment.
     1.3.1. The test manual shall list coverage requirements in detail.
